divs: Sighting DetailsAugust 29th 2011 9 PM until well after midnight (had work so had to go to sleep) We seen 27+ (so many we lost count) star like objects moving very fast across the sky,at about star height.They changed direction,hovered and would disappear,there was no sound. This was in Smyrna,TN. Bent Tree subdivision. Including myself there was 4 witnesses. Ages 20 to 60. We also seen a couple of regular planes go over but they were at plane height well below the star objects. I am working on getting a good high quality camera that will film these,this has been going on for awhile but last night there were more than I had ever seen!
Object Flight Path: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
